*Gross mass: 76,203 kg
*Empty mass: 4,000 kg
*Thrust (vac): 1,467 kN
*Isp (vac): 290 s (2.84 kN·s/kg)
*Isp (sea level): 256 s (2.51 kN·s/kg)
*Burn time: 138 s
*Diameter: 3.1 m
*Span: 3.1 m
*Length: 16.0 m
