*&quot;Posthumous Serenade&quot; (2017) (2-Disc Covers Album)
* &quot;More Posthumous Serenades&quot; (2018) (Covers Album)
* &quot;The VAST Companion&quot; (2018) (Non-fiction publication - stories behind VAST songs)

===Jon Crosby and the Resonator Band===
